comments: Hield (SAC) cleanly dislodges the ball from Jokic (DEN).
Murray (DEN) avoids making contact to Bogdanovic (SAC) as he legally contests his jump shot attempt.
Holmes (SAC) clamps Jokic's (DEN) arm that affects his ability to get to the rebound.
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Murray (DEN) and absorbs the contact.
Holmes (SAC) makes contact to Jokic's (DEN) body during his shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
Joseph (SAC) is not in the path of Jokic (DEN) when he sets the screen but the contact is marginal.
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Harris (DEN) and absorbs the contact during the screen.
Jokic (DEN) makes marginal contact with Hield (SAC) and doesn't affect his SQBR.
Joseph (SAC) makes marginal contact with Murray (DEN) and doesn't affect his SQBR.
Grant (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Joseph (SAC) and absorbs the contact.
Holmes (SAC) cleanly blocks Murray's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) makes clean contact to the ball as he attempts to get to the pass thrown from Barton (DEN).
Barnes (SAC) is established in the frontcourt when he tips the loose ball into the backcourt.  He then establishes position in the backcourt and gathers the ball, committing a backcourt violation.
Barton (DEN) makes contact to Hield's (SAC) arm, but the contact is marginal.
Hield (SAC) releases from Barton (DEN) prior to the shot attempt and does not dislodge Barton from his legally obtained position.
Barton (DEN) makes slight contact to Hield's (SAC) foot, but does not affect his ability to follow-through naturally after the jump shot attempt.
Joseph (SAC) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Barton (DEN) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Holmes (SAC) wraps Jokic (DEN) that affects his FOM during the rebound.
Barton (DEN) clamps Bogdanovic's (SAC) arm that affects his ability to defend.
Barton (DEN) makes marginal contact to Barnes' (SAC) arm during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Grant (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Bogdanovic (SAC) and absorbs the contact.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Bogdanovic (SAC) and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Harris (DEN) makes clean contact to the loose ball.
Harris (DEN) makes some contact to Barnes (SAC) arm, but does not affect his ability to get to the jump ball.
Bogdanovic (SAC) makes contact to Harris' (DEN) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Plumlee (DEN) commits a take foul on Barnes (SAC).
Grant (DEN) makes contact to Hield's (SAC) arm that affects his FOM.
Barnes (SAC) makes marginal contact to Murray (DEN) during his drive and doesn't affect his SQBR.
